{"title":"走迷宫","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2316","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>Morenan被困在了一个迷宫里。迷宫可以视为N个点M条边的有向图，其中Morenan处于起点S，迷宫的终点设为T。可惜的是，Morenan非常的脑小，<strong>他只会从一个点出发随机沿着一条从该点出发的有向边，到达另一个点。</strong>这样，Morenan走的步数可能很长，也可能是无限，更可能到不了终点。<strong>若到不了终点，则步数视为无穷大。</strong>但你必须想方设法求出Morenan所走步数的期望值。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第1行4个整数，N,M,S,T</p>\n<p>第[2, M+1]行每行两个整数o1, o2，表示有一条从o1到o2的边。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p align=\"left\">一个浮点数，保留小数点3位，为步数的期望值。若期望值为无穷大，则输出\"INF\"。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>6 6 1 6</p>\n<p>1 2</p>\n<p>1 3</p>\n<p>2 4</p>\n<p>3 5</p>\n<p>4 6</p>\n<p>5 6</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3.000</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>N&lt;=10000</p>\n<p>M&lt;=1000000</p>\n<p>保证强连通分量的大小不超过100</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}